Class GenericProcessor

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.unihd.dbs.uima.annotator.heideltime.processors.GenericProcessor
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    DecadeProcessor, HolidayProcessor

    public abstract class GenericProcessor
extends Object
    Abstract class to for all Processors to inherit from. A processor is a modular, self-sufficient piece of code that was added to HeidelTime to fulfill a specific function.

    julian zell
